    characterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ece41423a199ba04f8804d355c231cbb, type: 3}
    sentence: Hi, Jetty. You look really pretty in that outfit.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 1936918675910826544, guid: e8f1130d0e09cef45bb1f9ab49489848, type: 3}
    sentence: Hey, thank you. I like your fit too.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You\u2019re a performer, right? I wouldn\u2019t imagine that someone
      like you would struggle to meet new people. Why are you here?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Weird assumption that I do, and what do you mean someone like me?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You know, a showman, a communicator. Someone you wouldn\u2019t expect
      to meet here. Are you trying to improve your mind-reading skills or what?"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Yeah, I\u2019m not doing this first thing into a date."
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Oh, come on. Never been called out before?
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: I have but it seems like you need it more than I do, know-it-all. Counselor,
      I would like to leave please.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Wow, so easily offended and boring. I guess I want out too.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Jetty
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Great, have a great day.
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Ary
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: Right, see ya.
